Request to retrieve company base URL and then validate in the posthook.

hooks.body:
let companyCode = configuration['taleo.company.code'];

	done({request_vendor_path: "https://tbe.taleo.net/MANAGER/dispatcher/api/v1/serviceUrl/" + companyCode}); // username is provided as username@companyId so we add companyId to this URL
